Actions.Text: REFERRED TO VETERANS, HOMELAND SECURITY AND MILITARY AFFAIRS

Title: Relates to defining certain qualifying conditions for veterans
Summary: Relates to defining certain qualifying conditions for veterans; includes individuals licensed to provide health care services within the state of New York as someone a veteran may disclose military sexual trauma to.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to defining certain qualifying conditions for veterans
